author: Home Repair Tutor
description: I’m protecting this solid quartz curb top with Stay Put Surface Protector. The slip-resistant tacky backing keeps it in place and the blue surface is waterproof. It won’t leave residue behind and can be reused. It’s a great option for countertops as well.
